                  div.h-26.overflow-auto
                    div.pr-2.p-2
                      div.d-flex.justify-content-start.mb-3
                        div#chat_initial_messages.reply.text-black.white-break.rounded-lg.py-2.px-4.typing.bg-gray-200 I am an AI Assistant, Ask me anything, I will help answer your questions based on my understanding.
                      div.d-flex.justify-content-end.mb-3
                        div.text-white.rounded-lg.py-2.px-4.bg-question Hi
